118
00:09:08,213 --> 00:09:10,616
The running,
the boxing, everything.

119
00:09:10,649 --> 00:09:13,586
I was just his best companion in
those days. I was his best friend.

120
00:09:13,619 --> 00:09:18,658
We were that close, like salt and pepper.
Like salt and pepper.

121
00:09:23,028 --> 00:09:26,032
And it all begins here.
From the root to the fruit.

122
00:09:42,014 --> 00:09:44,049
Maryum, tell me something.

123
00:09:44,082 --> 00:09:46,085
When I started boxing,
