Most of the kids would laugh
at Muhammad.

166
00:12:03,088 --> 00:12:05,390
Say, "Cassius,
you can't do that."

167
00:12:05,423 --> 00:12:08,371
"That's too much for you to do.
You can't be that great."

168
00:12:08,961 --> 00:12:11,263
