Now, this is '58. So I hold my
hand on the phone and I says,

180
00:12:52,904 --> 00:12:56,431
"Willie, there's some sort of a nut
downstairs wants to talk to us."

181
00:13:02,881 --> 00:13:05,417
- It was a great meeting.
- Very interesting.

