00:32:27,511 --> 00:32:29,747
Then they taught
him about Snow White.

498
00:32:29,780 --> 00:32:33,985
Then there's the White House.

499
00:32:34,018 --> 00:32:37,655
When you look at television, you see
these two cars, one black and one white,

500
00:32:37,688 --> 00:32:40,591
and they put a gallon of gas
in each one...

501
00:32:42,693 --> 00:32:45,629
To see which car
can go the farthest.

502
00:32:45,662 --> 00:32:49,767
And every time the black car stopped
first and the white car just kept going.

503
00:32:49,800 --> 00:32:51,702
So this brainwashes the negro.
See?

504
00:32:51,735 --> 00:32:56,307
I always followed him,
got a chance to know him,

505
00:32:56,340 --> 00:32:59,377
got a chance to work with him.

506
00:32:59,410 --> 00:33:00,711
He was just a part of my life

507
00:33:00,744 --> 00:33:04,749
and, he goes back
as far as my memory goes.

508
00:33:21,765 --> 00:33:25,469
Clay's first taste of military life,
and quite possibly his only one,

509
00:33:25,502 --> 00:33:27,605
was at the induction,
or call-up centre,

510
00:33:27,638 --> 00:33:29,607
at the Old Post Office
building in Houston.

511
00:33:29,640 --> 00:33:32,076
Just before lunch.
It's all over.

