642
00:44:49,385 --> 00:44:51,188
"What?
Whoa. This kid is something."

643
00:44:51,221 --> 00:44:53,757
Yeah! Where's he at?

644
00:44:53,790 --> 00:44:57,795
I'm the king of the ring! I'm
the biggest thing in history!

645
00:44:59,195 --> 00:45:02,466
A young black kid with a
big mouth, talking sense.

646
00:45:02,499 --> 00:45:05,402
Yeah,
it was wonderful back then.

647
00:45:05,435 --> 00:45:08,338
I mean, they were still hanging
guys down in the South.

648
00:45:08,371 --> 00:45:13,844
Ali refused to be drafted
during the Vietnam War,

649
00:45:13,877 --> 00:45:15,045
and because of that

650
00:45:15,078 --> 00:45:20,250
he lost the very best boxing
years he had during that time

651
00:45:20,283 --> 00:45:22,753
because boxers
don't last forever.

652
00:45:24,187 --> 00:45:28,058
And so Lois,
who was the cover art director

653
00:45:28,091 --> 00:45:31,881
of Esquire magazine at the time, said,
