00:46:17,440 --> 00:46:22,112
"Yeah, yeah, Saint Sebastian."

667
00:46:22,145 --> 00:46:23,513
And I realized very quickly

668
00:46:23,546 --> 00:46:27,518
he was saying a Muslim
can't pose as a Christian.

669
00:46:29,285 --> 00:46:33,223
Whoa. Gotta do this cover.
What, what...

670
00:46:34,557 --> 00:46:36,860
"I can't do it."
"What can we do?"

671
00:46:36,893 --> 00:46:41,531
"Can we call Elijah Muhammad?"
