00:52:00,783 --> 00:52:03,486
So then he
started to, you know...

742
00:52:03,519 --> 00:52:06,156
And then tried to wind me up
a little bit, you know,

743
00:52:06,189 --> 00:52:10,260
and he said, "Trigger. You called me
Trigger, right? It was Trigger, right?"

