00:59:03,138 --> 00:59:04,340
The man's in trouble.

848
00:59:05,675 --> 00:59:10,012
Listen, George Foreman. People
are afraid of George Foreman.

849
00:59:10,045 --> 00:59:13,015
They talk about how hard he hits.
