01:01:05,360 --> 01:01:08,397
I could have heard him from New
York to Deer Lake, Pennsylvania

883
01:01:08,430 --> 01:01:09,699
without the phone.

884
01:01:09,732 --> 01:01:12,335
He said,
"But they're not Ali!"

885
01:01:16,171 --> 01:01:20,376
We flew Air Zaire. All black
people, all black pilots.

