01:36:12,933 --> 01:36:16,937
"He knows you." I said,"He knows me?
How does he know me, Cus?"

1426
01:36:20,240 --> 01:36:24,444
When I saw Muhammad Ali I was at a
reformatory in the Bronx, New York,

1427
01:36:24,477 --> 01:36:26,413
named Spofford.

